Hello Ethan

Today, I got to tell the world one about one of the most amazing things that has ever happened to me. It has nothing to do with raising money and everything to do with people, community, and what flows from the connections we make day by day.

I get to build with  and . Every day I get to wake up and strive to operate at the level of creativity and clarity of purpose that they bring to the table. It is one of the most incredible challenges I could ever hope for.

I get to build alongside , a community that has reshaped my life in a million ways over the past few years. A place that allowed me to connect the dots between the forums I modded as a teenager and what better forms of socialization could look like in the future.
And I get to do it with a vote of confidence from , where folks like     and more have been instrumental in encouraging me and the SIC team to take calculatedly ambitious swings

The  team is going to build you all something remarkable. And when it is all said and done, it will still be all about the only thing that matters: who we are when we’re connected to the people, places, and things that make us feel the most alive.
